headline: DryWater® Expands Nationwide with Walgreens -- Over 6,000 Locations Now Carry the Real Fruit Clean Hydration Brand
summary: DryWater®, the clean, real-fruit electrolyte + vitamin powder disrupting the hydration category, is making a major move into retail. Starting August 8th, DryWater will be available in over 2,000 Walgreens locations nationwide — with an additional 4,000+ doors joining the lineup later this year. This expansion puts DryWater in every major U.S. city, making it easier than ever for customers to grab clean hydration on the go.
